dropped.

18:17.638 --> 18:20.390
I'm the devil, bitch!
What, what?!

18:20.475 --> 18:23.810
[ fiddle plays ]

18:23.895 --> 18:26.605
Hey!
[ groans ]

18:29.233 --> 18:31.151
- Hey, Morty.
- Oh, oh, hey, Dad.

18:31.235 --> 18:34.112
Um, what... what are you doing
back from Pluto so quick?

18:34.197 --> 18:37.115
Uh... some people just
can't handle the truth.

18:37.200 --> 18:39.117
Especially dummies like me.

18:39.202 --> 18:41.661
Morty, I'm not as smart
as your grandpa Rick,

18:41.746 --> 18:44.998
