that your problem again.

18:45.082 --> 18:46.583
Hey, Dad.

18:46.667 --> 18:49.753
Nobody's smarter than Rick,
but nobody else is my Dad.

18:49.837 --> 18:51.546
You're a genius at that.

18:51.631 --> 18:53.548
Wow.
[ sniffles ]

18:53.633 --> 18:57.135
That's... humbling
and flattering, son.

18:57.220 --> 18:59.137
Thank you.

18:59.222 --> 19:01.503
What say we finish ourselves
an eight-planet solar system?

19:01.516 --> 19:03.850
Um... I'm just gonna
take this thing in

19:03.935 --> 19:05.852
and get an "A."
- Butter.

19:05.937 --> 19:07.562
- But...
- You're a genius...

19:07.647 --> 19:08.730
at being my Dad, Dad.

19:08.815 --> 19:10.065
Quit while you're ahead.

19:10.149 --> 19:11.733
And also, knock next time,
you know?

19:11.818 --> 19:13.298
I mean, I'm sitting in here,
I'm 14...

19:13.361 --> 19:14.861
I got a computer in here,
you know?

19:14.946 --> 19:16.696
Oh, I... I think
I understand.

19:16.781 --> 19:18.323
You're really playing with fire

19:18.407 --> 19:19.741
