like that, man.

19:19.826 --> 19:21.284
I get it. Say no more.

19:21.369 --> 19:22.786
I mean, one of these days,

19:22.870 --> 19:24.579
you know, you're gonna end
up seeing something.

19:24.664 --> 19:26.915
I got it!
Noted. Good night.

19:26.999 --> 19:29.835
[ metal music playing ]

19:29.919 --> 19:33.338
